{"tid":1754280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文長] 對於區議會選舉大勝嘅一啲睇法","createTime":"2019-11-25T07:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T07:23:01.000Z","uid":197157,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6a0b19b8a1375eb14ab15c299d28b6af73c006f7","tid":1754280,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:03:42.000Z","msg":"建制派潰敗，同上屆比更加係得返20%，而非建制派就多咗3倍議席<br />\n選票公佈大約係６：４（約167萬票對120.5萬票）<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我認為今次結果絕對值得開心，但記住唔好掉以輕心，要時刻保持清醒</span></strong><br />\n睇過一啲Post嘅睇法之後，有啲位我都想講吓自己睇法<br />\n<br />\n1. 今次係險勝，總票數唔係差好多咋！<br />\n其實我唔否定係險勝，因為總票數上大概只係得６：４<br />\n但係建制派嗰邊以往都會話有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">三十至四十萬</span></strong>係鐵票<br />\n拎最保守嘅30萬做標準，120.5萬減返30萬就淨返90.5萬<br />\n再重新計算一次比例就係約35%，更加莫講今次隨時唔止40萬鐵票<br />\n<br />\n2. 我哋係推到極限先贏到咋！（露晒底牌etc）<br />\n個人都幾認同今次非建制派真係出盡奶力，話係極限都唔過份<br />\n但係你估對家唔係極限咩？<br />\n由六月到依家經歷咗咁多事，佢哋會放水咩？<br />\n特衰政府咁想借今次選舉反映止暴制亂嘅民意，又會放水咩？<br />\n絕對唔會啊！<br />\n非建制派不斷叫人出去投票（網上呼籲），甚至有共識去投某啲候選人<br />\n同一時間，建制派都賤招盡出，而且愈做愈出面，愈做愈唔顧犯唔犯法<br />\n種票、海馬、掌心雷、旅遊巴接送，甚至有部份地方疑似出現長者優先<br />\n元朗重疑似有人拎刀喺票站出面企（有冇人可以話我知堅定流）<br />\n依家個事實就係大家都出盡全力，然後建制派都係輸咗<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而最重要嘅係！</span></span></strong><br />\n佢哋班友做嘅嘢係舞弊、犯法！！<br />\n即係佢哋係出撚埋矛招，犯撚埋法都輸啊<br />\n<br />\n3. 今次佢哋輸咗，下次選舉一定更難贏啦<br />\n冇錯，今次區選大勝一定會令建制派提高警覺，開始準備下次選舉<br />\n但係咁唔代表我哋唔可以開始準備喎<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">贏咗一定係開心，但千祈唔好輕敵，要及早準備下一個選舉！</span></strong></span><br />\n文宣唔一定係選舉嗰個月先可以做，平時都做吓文宣一樣係極為有用！<br />\n緊記！贏定輸除咗睇建制派做咗幾多準備，同時都要睇吓非建制派做咗幾多準備<br />\n<br />\n4. 今次區議會選舉大勝嘅意義<br />\n想簡單講吓我覺得今次區選大勝有咩意義<br />\na. 話畀其他人知，同時亦畀自己知道香港目前嘅主流民意係點（再次證明）<br />\nb. 承上，以後唔需要再因為擔心自己係少數而唔敢出聲<br />\nc. 和勇不割嘅最佳佐證<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">d. 證明香港人只要齊心，再難嘅事都做得到！今次係第一次，但唔會係最後一次！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後，連登生日快樂<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n天佑香港<br />\n天佑理工手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">同樣今日生日，我順便都想乞句生日快樂</span></span>"},{"pid":"52fbee69803e5e1b5cc749c3ca8e7685a0917604","tid":1754280,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:04:47.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[元朗屏山北][搞大佢]區選仲未完仲可以再爭取!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754167\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754167</a>"},{"pid":"269b18bb30f80ed8e614aac144e6fa903bdac43e","tid":1754280,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:05:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2f4b6946761d1ebaa2300e869fdf144d2bfc684","tid":1754280,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:06:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"560d709e8a68f8f00550f0bb3623aa48352a69ea","tid":1754280,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:06:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"276c9f355630ee55541c39088ed15b5222ae577d","tid":1754280,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122c2ef683980a81beb6543051d66adec1afd383","tid":1754280,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:07:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fbb81c60247de811f80ef99cd902a79631708ea2","tid":1754280,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:07:21.000Z","msg":"建制呢種反人類思維，已唔配有資格同我地做對手，我們思維比他們進化很多。牛同人的分別。"},{"pid":"c009e84ebc67468ad129bc95197367f2fbe1acaa","tid":1754280,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbb81c60247de811f80ef99cd902a79631708ea2","tid":1754280,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:07:21.000Z","msg":"建制呢種反人類思維，已唔配有資格同我地做對手，我們思維比他們進化很多。牛同人的分別。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:08:55.000Z","msg":"呢樣嘢你同我知，對面個單眼佬都知<br />\n今次係一個令其他人都清醒嘅機會<br />\n我唔奢求全部人因此清醒，但多得一個得一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300455a2f27eb73294c98cec50d2558aa861106d","tid":1754280,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"276c9f355630ee55541c39088ed15b5222ae577d","tid":1754280,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:09:11.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6892ab551d955c79ad3678e8959b21e4f7081574","tid":1754280,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:10:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdc565ad1e8485558439623ec383dbf3eed81124","tid":1754280,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:11:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2957126015dd8da925d81b23c00c113402b7b4b6","tid":1754280,"uid":65183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"真係唔好掉以輕心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0583bf3ecefb9feb4fb503c4024baf2d170db2c3","tid":1754280,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:13:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36fbb5d4d362da47c91b069557681bef09e7887a","tid":1754280,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2957126015dd8da925d81b23c00c113402b7b4b6","tid":1754280,"uid":65183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"真係唔好掉以輕心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:13:56.000Z","msg":"真！<br />\n今次贏，下次都要贏！<br />\n成功嘅地方要繼續，有錯嘅地方要改善！"},{"pid":"5d39013d5f896d347a2aff2f32dc13ce231e3178","tid":1754280,"uid":114154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:15:08.000Z","msg":"今次仲有手足因為無報名而無投票資格<br />\n<br />\n下次2020立法會選舉更加重要<br />\n唔該你地醒返少少記得報名做選民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52759d6835e9a31db2e5e8c60542e6495472f54a","tid":1754280,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d39013d5f896d347a2aff2f32dc13ce231e3178","tid":1754280,"uid":114154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:15:08.000Z","msg":"今次仲有手足因為無報名而無投票資格<br />\n<br />\n下次2020立法會選舉更加重要<br />\n唔該你地醒返少少記得報名做選民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:16:29.000Z","msg":"呢樣我都有諗過<br />\n而再下次嘅區議會就更加唔使講，好多本身唔夠18歲嘅人終於都可以投票<br />\n我同政府、建制派、高官唔一樣，對年輕一代充滿信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b923e4a1ce0cdafc03bd46469714ade2d347b9b","tid":1754280,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:16:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a613f7f3c7ebeadc6e24ad90d6991124271ec99c","tid":1754280,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:17:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ee05e30f6a0729466ecd560f0a3a0b06199b068","tid":1754280,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:17:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea8a792e9f5c2e94d1bb8c663986189e71787bf1","tid":1754280,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T07:18:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e296b71ed44980a9ffe7034180343d8e13328767","tid":1754280,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"